snippet.title: Fantasy General gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Fantasy General, Dos PC game produced by Mindscape in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/fantasy-general/1059/
Playing the first two mission in the campaign mode, leading to victory.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
